"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon-star size-4\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 5h4\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></span></span></span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute top-1/2 flex size-4 -translate-y-1/2 items-center justify-center transition-[left,right,opacity,transform,color] duration-200 right-[0.72rem] text-slate-500/75 dark:text-indigo-100/85\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2.1\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-moon-star size-3.5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M18 5h4\"></path><path d=\"M20 3v4\"></path><path d=\"M20.985 12.486a9 9 0 1 1-9.473-9.472c.405-.022.617.46.402.803a6 6 0 0 0 8.268 8.268c.344-.215.825-.004.803.401\"></path></svg></span><span class=\"sr-only\">Toggle color theme</span></button><a class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#4d35ef_0%,#432dd7_100%)] text-white shadow-[0_14px_40px_rgba(67,45,215,0.28)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_20px_54px_rgba(67,45,215,0.36)] text-sm h-10 px-4\" href=\"/contact\">Contact Us</a></div><div class=\"lg:hidden\"><button class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-border/80 bg-secondary/70 text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.24)] backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:border-primary/20 hover:bg-secondary text-sm size-10 rounded-full p-0\" aria-label=\"Open menu\" type=\"button\" aria-haspopup=\"dialog\" aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-controls=\"radix-_R_99lb_\" data-state=\"closed\"><svg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" class=\"lucide lucide-menu size-5\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M4 5h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 12h16\"></path><path d=\"M4 19h16\"></path></svg></button></div></div></div></header><main id=\"content\" class=\"flex-1\"><section class=\"relative overflow-hidden pt-32 sm:pt-36 lg:pt-40 lg:pb-24 pb-16 sm:pb-20\"><div aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden\"><div class=\"absolute top-[-10%] left-[18%] h-64 w-64 rounded-full bg-[var(--hero-orbit)] blur-3xl md:h-80 md:w-80\"></div><div class=\"absolute top-[6%] right-[12%] h-56 w-56 rounded-full bg-[var(--hero-spotlight)] blur-3xl md:h-72 md:w-72\"></div><div class=\"absolute inset-x-[18%] top-[-14%] h-72 rounded-full bg-white/28 blur-3xl dark:bg-white/6\"></div></div><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"pointer-events-none h-full w-full fill-current stroke-current hero-grid-mask absolute inset-0 text-foreground/10\"><defs><pattern id=\"_R_9av5ulb_\" width=\"44\" height=\"44\" patternUnits=\"userSpaceOnUse\" x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\"><path d=\"M.5 44V.5H44\" fill=\"none\" stroke-dasharray=\"0\"></path></pattern></defs><rect width=\"100%\" height=\"100%\" fill=\"url(#_R_9av5ulb_)\"></rect><svg x=\"-1\" y=\"-1\" class=\"overflow-visible\"></svg></svg><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 bottom-0 h-28 bg-gradient-to-b from-transparent to-background\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative\"><div class=\"max-w-5xl\"><div class=\"space-y-6\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-primary/40 bg-primary text-white backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.4]\">Contact</div><div class=\"space-y-4 sm:space-y-5\"><h1 class=\"hero-title max-w-5xl\">Start with the problem shape.</h1><p class=\"copy-lg max-w-3xl\">A short, thoughtful brief is enough.</p></div><div class=\"grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 sm:max-w-3xl\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">Current state</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">What is changing</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.3rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/38 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground/66\">Where judgment matters most</div></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"section-space\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid gap-8 lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_0.95fr]\"><div class=\"section-frame px-6 py-8 md:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">Inquiry form</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">A premium handoff, not a generic lead form.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Validated server-side and posted to a configurable webhook.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8\"><form class=\"space-y-5\" action=\"\" encType=\"multipart/form-data\" method=\"POST\"><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"$ACTION_REF_1\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"$ACTION_1:0\" value=\"{&quot;id&quot;:&quot;60b779936df2f958c2a975ea5ec47dfef791b3df58&quot;,&quot;bound&quot;:&quot;$@1&quot;}\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"$ACTION_1:1\" value=\"[{&quot;status&quot;:&quot;idle&quot;,&quot;message&quot;:&quot;$undefined&quot;,&quot;errors&quot;:{},&quot;values&quot;:{&quot;name&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;email&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;company&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;projectType&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;brief&quot;:&quot;&quot;}}]\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"$ACTION_KEY\" value=\"k4a795ac4203fe0dbfb42e6ebaa7464b1\"/><input type=\"hidden\" name=\"source\" value=\"/contact\"/><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><label class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/84\" for=\"name\">Name</label><input class=\"flex h-12 w-full rounded-2xl border border-border/80 bg-background/70 px-4 text-sm text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.16)] outline-none backdrop-blur-md backdrop-saturate-[1.4] transition placeholder:text-foreground/40 focus-visible:border-primary/40 focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-primary/10 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50\" id=\"name\" placeholder=\"Alicia Chen\" aria-invalid=\"false\" name=\"name\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><label class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/84\" for=\"email\">Email</label><input type=\"email\" class=\"flex h-12 w-full rounded-2xl border border-border/80 bg-background/70 px-4 text-sm text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.16)] outline-none backdrop-blur-md backdrop-saturate-[1.4] transition placeholder:text-foreground/40 focus-visible:border-primary/40 focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-primary/10 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50\" id=\"email\" placeholder=\"alicia@company.com\" aria-invalid=\"false\" name=\"email\" value=\"\"/></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-5 sm:grid-cols-2\"><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><label class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/84\" for=\"company\">Company or team</label><input class=\"flex h-12 w-full rounded-2xl border border-border/80 bg-background/70 px-4 text-sm text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.16)] outline-none backdrop-blur-md backdrop-saturate-[1.4] transition placeholder:text-foreground/40 focus-visible:border-primary/40 focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-primary/10 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50\" id=\"company\" placeholder=\"Sonicverse\" name=\"company\" value=\"\"/></div><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><label class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/84\" for=\"projectType\">Project type</label><select id=\"projectType\" name=\"projectType\" class=\"flex h-12 w-full rounded-2xl border border-border/80 bg-background/70 px-4 text-sm text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.16)] outline-none transition focus-visible:border-primary/40 focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-primary/10\"><option value=\"\" selected=\"\">Select an area</option><option value=\"Product engineering\">Product engineering</option><option value=\"Web platform\">Web platform</option><option value=\"Design system\">Design system</option><option value=\"Open-source tooling\">Open-source tooling</option><option value=\"Technical architecture\">Technical architecture</option></select></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2.5\"><label class=\"text-sm font-medium text-foreground/84\" for=\"brief\">Project brief</label><textarea class=\"flex min-h-32 w-full rounded-[1.4rem] border border-border/80 bg-background/70 px-4 py-3 text-sm text-foreground shadow-[inset_0_1px_0_rgba(255,255,255,0.16)] outline-none transition placeholder:text-foreground/40 focus-visible:border-primary/40 focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-primary/10 disabled:cursor-not-allowed disabled:opacity-50\" id=\"brief\" name=\"brief\" placeholder=\"We need a modern platform foundation with a premium public site and a calmer delivery path for the next release cycle.\" aria-invalid=\"false\"></textarea><p class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-foreground/52\">Share the shape of the system, what is changing, and what a good outcome looks like.</p></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between\"><div class=\"text-sm leading-6 text-foreground/56\">A thoughtful brief is enough for a strong first conversation.</div><button class=\"inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full border font-medium whitespace-nowrap transition-all duration-200 outline-none select-none focus-visible:border-ring focus-visible:ring-3 focus-visible:ring-ring/40 disabled:pointer-events-none disabled:opacity-50 [&amp;_svg]:pointer-events-none [&amp;_svg]:size-4 border-transparent bg-[linear-gradient(135deg,#4d35ef_0%,#432dd7_100%)] text-white shadow-[0_14px_40px_rgba(67,45,215,0.28)] hover:-translate-y-0.5 hover:shadow-[0_20px_54px_rgba(67,45,215,0.36)] h-12 px-6 text-[0.95rem]\" type=\"submit\">Send inquiry</button></div></form></div></div><div class=\"space-y-6\"><div class=\"section-frame px-6 py-8 md:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">What to include</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">Helpful prompts</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Any of these is enough to start a practical conversation.</p></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 grid gap-3\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.35rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/44 px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/66\">A new product needs a sober technical foundation.</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.35rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/44 px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/66\">An existing platform is carrying too much accidental complexity.</div><div class=\"rounded-[1.35rem] border border-border/60 bg-background/44 px-4 py-4 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/66\">A team wants to turn internal patterns into stable reusable systems.</div></div></div><div class=\"section-frame px-6 py-8 md:px-8\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-primary/40 bg-primary text-white backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.4]\">Direct contact</div><div class=\"mt-5 space-y-3 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/66\"><p>hello@sonicverse.eu</p><p>Open-source-first product engineering and software systems.</p></div></div></div></div></section><section class=\"pb-24 sm:pb-28\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl space-y-5\"><div class=\"inline-flex items-center rounded-full border px-3 py-1 text-[0.72rem] font-medium tracking-[0.13em] uppercase transition-colors border-border/70 bg-background/52 text-foreground/62 backdrop-blur-sm backdrop-saturate-[1.3]\">FAQ</div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><h2 class=\"section-title\">A few expectations, upfront.</h2><p class=\"section-copy\">Enough context to make the first conversation more useful.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"grid gap-6 lg:grid-cols-3\"><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">What kinds of teams do you work with?</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">Teams where product quality and engineering quality need to move together.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">Do you only work on open-source projects?</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">No. Open source is part of the approach, not a limit on the work.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"\" style=\"opacity:0;transform:translateY(18px)\"><div class=\"rounded-[1.9rem] border border-border/70 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] shadow-[var(--shadow-soft)] backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.6] h-full\"><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-3 p-6 sm:p-8\"><h3 class=\"text-[1.75rem] leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.025em] text-foreground\">What helps a first conversation go well?</h3><p class=\"text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/68\">A short brief: current state, pressure points, and what success looks like next.</p></div></div></div></div></div></section><!--$--><!--/$--></main><footer class=\"relative overflow-hidden border-t border-border/60 bg-[linear-gradient(180deg,var(--surface-1),var(--surface-2))] py-14 backdrop-blur-xl backdrop-saturate-[1.5]\"><div class=\"absolute inset-x-0 top-0 h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-primary/28 to-transparent\"></div><div class=\"mx-auto w-full max-w-7xl px-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 space-y-10\"><div class=\"grid gap-8 md:grid-cols-[1.2fr_0.8fr_0.8fr]\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-3\"><img src=\"/icon-purple.svg\" class=\"h-8 w-auto text-primary/70\" alt=\"\" aria-hidden=\"true\" loading=\"eager\" decoding=\"async\"/><p class=\"font-heading text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-foreground/62\">Sonicverse</p></div><h2 class=\"max-w-md text-3xl leading-[1.08] font-medium tracking-[-0.03em] text-balance\">Modern software systems, digital products, and open-source technology.</h2><p class=\"max-w-xl text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/62\">Built with strong engineering taste, open collaboration, and a preference for systems that stay understandable as they grow.</p></div><div><p class=\"mb-4 text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.04em] text-foreground/76\">Navigation</p><div class=\"grid gap-2 text-sm text-foreground/62\"><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/\">Home</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/about\">About</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/blog\">Blog</a><a class=\"hover:text-foreground\" href=\"/projects\">Projects</a></div></div><div class=\"space-y-4\"><p class=\"text-sm font-semibold tracking-[0.04em] text-foreground/76\">Contact</p><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm leading-7 text-foreground/62\"><p>hello@sonicverse.eu</p><p>Open collaboration, careful delivery, and long-term technical thinking.</p></div></div></div><div data-orientation=\"horizontal\" role=\"none\" class=\"shrink-0 bg-border/80 h-px w-full\"></div><div class=\"flex flex-col gap-2 text-sm text-foreground/48 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between\"><p>Open source by default. Built to be readable, maintainable, and calm.</p><p>Cloudflare-ready Next.js App Router implementation.</p></div></div></footer></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/05tsy9pxtuyv0.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[89554,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/148d-9g_w8i0~.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04mq052otkkl9.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0q77_8lbj.p8k.js\\\"],\\\"ThemeProvider\\\"]\\n3:I[58956,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/148d-9g_w8i0~.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/04mq052otkkl9.js\\\",\\\"/_n